#

Classic Egg Salad Sandwich

25 min
$5.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

eggsglutendairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Lunch

Tags:

sandwicheasylunch

Description

A creamy and flavorful egg salad packed between soft bread, perfect for a quick lunch.

Ingredients

  • eggs: 4 large
  • mayonnaise: 1/4 cup
  • mustard: 1 tablespoon
  • celery: 1/4 cup, diced
  • green onion: 1/4 cup, diced
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • bread: 4 slices
